<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīmūlastānaṁ mallikhārjunadēvarakunu
<lb n="2"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīśakavaruṣaṁbbulu 1407 Agu nēṁṭi viśvā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>vasusaṁ<supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied>tsara mārggaśira ba 3 gu saṁtēśvarakomāragu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ruvumahāpātṛla komāruṁḍu tirumaladā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>sumahāpātṛṁḍu samarppiṁccina Āvulanu
<lb n="6"/>ṟēpaṭipūṁṭa pālu maddhyeraṁggaṁmīṁdaṁ baḍa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṁ bidukuvāru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> māpaṭipālu dēvaraku samarppiṁcci
<lb n="8"/>tammaḷavāru Anubhaviṁcuvāru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yīyāvula kōḍelanu
<lb n="9"/>Āṁbōtulaṁ jēśidi <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> peyyalanu kadupunaṁ gūrci
<lb n="10" break="no"/>di <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yī mariyyādanu ceyyaka tammaḷavāru tappirā
<lb n="11"/>vāri ṟommunanu yīśvaruni trisūlaṁ viṟugu
<lb n="12" break="no"/>nu<note n="197-1">The inscription below this line is built in into a</note> [*] yī yāvulanu voḍḍerājulu tuṟukarāju
<lb n="13" break="no"/>lu karaṇarājulu teluṁgurājulu vīrala pa
<lb n="14" break="no"/>nulavāru yevvaru ganaka Apahariṁcinānu gō
<lb n="15" break="no"/>hatya braṁhmatya sēsina dōṣānaṁ bōvuvārū <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

